`corcovado`, `copa`, `neoism-terminal-core`, `neoism-backend`, and parts of
`neoism-window` are derived from Rio. Neoism extends the sugarloaf renderer with
additional first-party subsystems (notably the virtual-surface editor/markdown/
agent rendering path and shader overlay); the Rio-derived code remains under
